			"body": "<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: summarize by coderabbit.ai -->\n<!-- walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>📝 Walkthrough</summary>\n\n## Walkthrough\n\nAdded sanitisation and tests for Unicode directional isolate characters; updated mobile plugin asset manifest hashes and embedded abc SVG post-processing to set viewBox when width/height are numeric; modified CodeMirror setup to move bidi-isolate handling into a new view plugin that marks isolate characters.\n\n## Changes\n\n|Cohort / File(s)|Summary|\n|---|---|\n|**Character sanitisation & tests** <br> `packages/lib/utils/replaceUnsupportedCharacters.ts`, `packages/lib/utils/replaceUnsupportedCharacters.test.ts`|Replaces directional isolate characters U+2066–U+2069 with `\\uFFFD` (in addition to existing NUL handling). Added tests for individual isolates, sequences, and mixed NUL+isolate inputs.|\n|**CodeMirror bidi handling** <br> `packages/editor/CodeMirror/createEditor.ts`, `packages/editor/CodeMirror/extensions/biDirectionalTextExtension.ts`|Excluded bidi isolate code points from the editor's `highlightSpecialChars` regex and introduced a `ViewPlugin` that finds isolate openers (`\\u2066-\\u2068`), creates `Decoration.mark` entries, exposes `isolatedRanges`, and registers via `EditorView.bidiIsolatedRanges`.|\n|**Mobile plugin assets & SVG post-processing** <br> `packages/app-mobile/pluginAssets/abc/abc_render.js.base64.js`, `packages/app-mobile/pluginAssets/index.js`, `packages/app-mobile/pluginAssets/index.web.js`|Embedded ABC renderer now post-processes rendered containers to set `viewBox` on `svg` elements when numeric finite `width` and `height` exist and `viewBox` is absent. Updated exported asset manifest `hash` values in both mobile manifests.|\n\n## Suggested labels\n\n`editor`, `mobile`\n\n## Suggested reviewers\n\n- personalizedrefrigerator\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- walkthrough_end -->\n\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>🚥 Pre-merge checks | ✅